    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，B节点有两条分支。一条是通过chain关系指向C，也就是另一个Retail_OrderManagement处理节点；另一条是通过attestation关系指向Retail_CustomerLoyalty。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty",
        "chain",
        "attestation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把B节点的两条分支画好了。chain到C，attestation到D。现在C和D都指向同一个地方吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，C和D都要汇聚到E，这是一个关于Retail_CustomerLoyalty的判断节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_OrderManagement",
        "Retail_CustomerLoyalty"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "E节点是判断节点，那它的输出条件是什么？我看需要yes和no两条分支。",
